 Liposomal Doxorubicin and Docetaxel in HER2 Negative Metastatic Breast Cancer@highlight

This is an open phase II multicentre study evaluating the efficacy and safety of the non pegylated liposomal doxorubicin (Myocet(R)) and docetaxel (Taxotere(R)) combination as first-line treatment of patients with metastatic HER2/neu negative breast cancer.

